<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figure 9. Map of Eastern Brazil showing distribution of I. ensiformis, I. fasciculata, I. kraholandica, I. longirostra, I. revoluta, I. scopulina, I. veadeirosii, and I. walteri." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.88.12891.figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/160691" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">9</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
